WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
Have you ever wondered if we ever go inside a black hole?

2
00:00:03.500 --> 00:00:05.700
What will we see inside the black hole?

3
00:00:05.700 --> 00:00:12.000
NASA has recently released this video in which it is shown what kind of view you will see if you go inside the black hole.

4
00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:14.300
In this video, Sagittarius.

5
00:00:14.300 --> 00:00:18.000
A black hole is shown which is in the center of our Milky Way galaxy.

6
00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:21.500
And its mass is 43 million times more than our sun.

7
00:00:21.500 --> 00:00:26.300
Basically this is a beautiful sight of death which has been created by the Discover supercomputer.

